com.cognex.dataman.sdk

Interface DataManSystem.OnImageDataArrivedListener

  • Enclosing class:
    DataManSystem

    public static interface DataManSystem.OnImageDataArrivedListener
    Interface definition for a callback to be invoked when a read image is arrived and the image should be returned as a byte array.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void onImageDataArrived(DataManSystem dataManSystem, int resultId, byte[] imageData)
      Called when an image has been arrived.

    • Method Detail

      • onImageDataArrived

        void onImageDataArrived(DataManSystem dataManSystem,
                        int resultId,
                        byte[] imageData)
        Called when an image has been arrived.
        Parameters:
        dataManSystem - The DataManSystem object that invoked the callback.
        resultId - The identifier of the result. This value can be used to match the read string with the other result types like images, image graphics or XML results.
        imageData - The image as byte array that arrived from the reader.
